{"tid":35193,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美研究稱小說情節多如牛毛，但其實基本“套路”只有六種。","createTime":"2016-12-12T02:30:11.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-21T02:32:46.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"74159ee9439046253b31423c29a88f0ac572d1c7","tid":35193,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T02:30:11.000Z","msg":"美國研究人員說，小說情節多如牛毛，但其實基本&ldquo;套路&rdquo;只有六種。 <br />\n<br />\n佛蒙特大學數學系博士安迪&middot;里根和同事利用人工智能程序分析1327本書，這其中既包括兒童讀物，也包括莎翁戲劇以及經典小說。 <br />\n<br />\n人工智能程序分析了小說中的&ldquo;情感軌跡&rdquo;而非情節後發現，小說&ldquo;套路&rdquo;無非六種：由窮到富、由富到窮、先苦後甜、先甜後苦、先甜後苦再甜、先苦後甜又苦。其中，由窮到富這樣白手起家的故事是狄更斯、奧斯汀等小說家的最愛，但讀者們似乎更偏愛後幾種。 <br />\n<br />\n　　英國《每日郵報》援引里根的話報道，小說幫助人類理解自身的存在，他們的研究有一天可以幫助科學家&ldquo;訓練&rdquo;電腦來寫小說。"},{"pid":"c50f123f8541162d316cc6e23f9abd3ea301ad62","tid":35193,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T02:07:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d492430f56602c0977b94ebef40f74d464cac14","tid":35193,"uid":683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T02:10:12.000Z","msg":"on9，得一種套路：起承轉合<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e74dda7fdd02c08bacb3099f8a3b9fd1